MPS demo project

Steps to open the project in MPS:
1. clone the repository
2. start MPS
3. open the project through the STM.mpr project file
4. In File -> Settings -> Path Variables add an STM_PROJECT_ROOT variable pointing to the root directory of the project
5. Close and re-open the project for MPS to pick the new values
6. In the "Project View" panel on the left hand side of the screen select the four language nodes (icons with capital letter L), right-click and choose "Rebuild Selected Modules"
7. Select the two solution nodes (icons with capital letter S), right-click and choose "Rebuild Selected Modules"
8. Now you should be able to run the solutions in the STM_sandbox module as well as create your own ones
